{"title":"Royal Racing is Back with  New Limited-Edition Core Gloves","link":"https://bikerumor.com/royal-racing-is-back-new-limited-edition-core-gloves/","date":1730901600000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Innes Graham)\" /></p>\n<p>After a post-Covid hiatus, the UK’s Royal Racing is back with a new Limited-Edition Series of its popular Core Gloves. As a brand that prides itself on making a “no-nonsense kit for the real rider”, these new gloves promise to be “versatile and comfortable with the Royal Racing styling turned up to the max.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Royal Racing LE Core Gloves green\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-green-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Innes Graham)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Core Gloves seem to be a staple item for Royal. The Core Series offers all-around performance with what appears to be a lightweight design with minimal padding or extras. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Royal Racing LE Core Gloves Barbed wire\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Barbed-wire-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Royal Racing LE Core Gloves black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-black-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Royal Racing LE Core Gloves zebra\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-zebra-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Royal Racing’s Limited-Edition Core gloves are available in various styles, with limited-edition graphics, so riders can decide to make a statement or keep things low-key. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Royal Racing LE Core Gloves Pink\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-Pink-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Royal-Racing-LE-Core-Gloves-purple-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" 