 for max grip</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Secure hook and loop closure</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Moulded cuff for security</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://royalracing.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RoyalRacing.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/royal-racing-is-back-new-limited-edition-core-gloves/\">Royal Racing is Back with  New Limited-Edition Core Gloves</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9885b0c3fa048b2b9c79fcce58a4a02db9f005f048099f64a22714b3b2e348e0","category":"Cycling"}